# Components (Portal)

Atomic: `atoms/` → `molecules/` → `organisms/` → `templates/` (+ `components/tournament/` domain)

- `QueryState` (`molecules/QueryState`) cho loading/error/empty
- `PermissionGate` (`atoms/PermissionGate`) — không render admin action khi thiếu quyền
- `Modal`, `ConfirmDialog`, `GlassPanel`, `StatCard` — tái dùng thay markup lặp
- Tailwind + `ThemeProvider` + `config/theme.ts` — không hardcode `#hex` / `rgb()`
- Props typed explicitly — không `any`
- Max **400 effective lines** per file — `pnpm size-gate:strict`

```tsx
type ModerationActionBarProps = {
  selectedCount: number;
  onApprove: () => void;
  onReject: () => void;
  disabled?: boolean;
};

export function ModerationActionBar({ selectedCount, onApprove, onReject, disabled }: ModerationActionBarProps) {
  return (
    <PermissionGate permission="moderation:write">
      <div className="border-border flex items-center gap-2">
        <Button onClick={onApprove} disabled={disabled || selectedCount === 0}>Duyệt</Button>
        <Button variant="danger" onClick={onReject} disabled={disabled || selectedCount === 0}>Từ chối</Button>
      </div>
    </PermissionGate>
  );
}
```

Logic nặng → `lib/tournament/` hoặc hook; component chỉ render + event wiring.
